{"tid":1045372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔識點樣同 令我唔開心嘅人相處","createTime":"2019-03-03T14:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:42:09.000Z","uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a85c7b7d7aff87cd250408dfe82b18419e2122d","tid":1045372,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"就算我份人幾正面<br />\n我點樣 分享用另一個角度睇世界<br />\n佢哋唔會改變不但止<br />\n只係睇到我缺點<br />\n我唔明白<br />\n我係一個簡單嘅人<br />\n我要求亦都唔高<br />\n無論對人的對自己亦都唔會太過份<br />\n簡單就係快樂<br />\n同埋要多欣賞自己同對方嘅優點<br />\n<br />\n但咁耐以嚟我覺得我改變唔到對方<br />\n我亦都變得不再正面<br />\n其實係心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個心好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7983b48b37f2e2d9b468c3303bd8021ab0bd50b","tid":1045372,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔遠離佢地"},{"pid":"59d6a0c004f5304593eee8c8bdf97beb76b40d38","tid":1045372,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7983b48b37f2e2d9b468c3303bd8021ab0bd50b","tid":1045372,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔遠離佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"家家有本難念的經"}]}